title: Softball to Host Louisiana Tech - University of North Texas Athletics - Mean Green Sports
content: Softball to Host Louisiana Tech - University of North Texas Athletics  Mean Green Sports
description: DENTON – North Texas softball will host Louisiana Tech April 14-16 at Lovelace Stadium. The Mean Green (24-8, 12-3) are coming off a midweek win over Stephen F. Austin Tuesday night and will play the Lady Techsters (27-15, 7-5) looking to extend their six-game home winning streak.
